temFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi0dpiuk1tvi\">首先，得确保你的电脑已安装 Docker 并处于运行状态，同时需要 Python 3.12 或更高版本。然后，按照如下安装步骤：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 通过pipx安装Strix</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">pipx install strix-agent</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 配置AI服务提供商（如OpenAI）</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">export</span>&nbsp;STRIX_LLM=<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"openai/gpt-5\"</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">export</span>&nbsp;LLM_API_KEY=<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"your-api-key\"</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 运行首次安全评估</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">strix --target ./app-directory</span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi0dpiuk1li7\">有进阶用法，对于需要身份验证的灰盒测试，可以使用自定义指令：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">strix</span>&nbsp;--target <a href=\"https://your-app.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://your-app.com</a> --instruction&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"使用凭证user:pass执行身份验证测试\"</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi0dpiuk1m4w\">在CI/CD环境中，可以使用非交互模式：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\">strix -n --target&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">https</span>:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//your-app.com</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi0dpiuky1d\">首次运行时会自动下载沙盒 Docker 镜像，测试结果将保存到 agent_runs/&lt;运行名称&gt;目录中。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"js_darkmode__44\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &q